\c 26
\s Dhavhidhi anorambazve kuuraya Sauro
\p
\v 1 Zvino VaZifi vakauya kuna Sauro paGibhiya vachiti: Dhavhidhi haasi wakavanda pachikomo cheHakira paJeshimoni here?
\v 2 Zvino Sauro wakasimuka ndokuburukira kurenje reZifi ane vanhu vakasarudzwa vekwaIsiraeri zvuru zvitatu, kuti atsvake Dhavhidhi murenje reZifi.
\v 3 Zvino Sauro wakavaka musasa pachikomo cheHakira, chiri mberi kweJeshimoni panzira. Asi Dhavhidhi wakagara murenje, ndokuona kuti Sauro anomutevera murenje.
\v 4 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakatuma vashori kuti azive kuti Sauro wasvika zvirokwazvo.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakasimuka ndokusvika panzvimbo Sauro paaiva avaka musasa, Dhavhidhi ndokuona nzvimbo Sauro paaiva arere, naAbhineri mwanakomana waNeri, mukuru wehondo yake. Zvino Sauro waiva arere pakakombwa nengoro, uye rudzi rwaiva rwavaka musasa rwakamukomba.
\v 6 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakapindura, ndokutaura kuna Ahimereki muHiti, nekuna Abhishai mwanakomana waZeruya munin'ina waJoabhu achiti: Ndiani achaburuka neni kuna Sauro kumusasa? Abhishai ndokuti: Ini ndini ndichaburuka nemwi.
\v 7 Naizvozvo Dhavhidhi naAbhishai vakasvika kuvanhu usiku, zvino tarira, Sauro waiva arere hope pakakombwa nengoro, uye pfumo rake raiva rakabayirwa muvhu kumutsamhiro wake; naAbhineri nevanhu vaiva vakarara vakamukomba.
\v 8 Zvino Abhishai wakati kuna Dhavhidhi: Mwari wakavharira muvengi wako muruoko rwako nhasi; naizvozvo zvino regai henyu ndimubaire muvhu pamwe nepfumo, handingapamhi kwaari.
\v 9 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakati kuna Abhishai: Usamuparadza, nokuti ndiani angagona kutambanudzira ruoko rwake kumuzodzwa waJehovha akasava nemhosva?
\v 10 Dhavhidhi akatizve: NaJehovha mupenyu, asi Jehovha achamurova, kana kuti kusvike zuva rake rekufa, zvimwe achaburukira kunorwa akaparadzwa.
\v 11 Ngazvive kure neni, naJehovha, kutambanudzira ruoko rwangu kurwisa muzodzwa waJehovha; asi tora hako pfumo riri kumutsamhiro wake, nechirongo chemvura, tiende.
\v 12 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakatora pfumo nechirongo chemvura kuzvibvisa kumutsamhiro, vakaenda. Zvino hakuna wakaona, hakuna wakaziva, hakuna wakamuka, nokuti vese vaiva varere, nokuti hope dzinorema dzaJehovha dzaiva dzavawira.
\p
\v 13 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakayambukira mhiri, ndokumira panhongonya yechikomo ari kure; paiva nechinhabwe chikuru pakati pavo.
\v 14 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakadanidzira kuvanhu nekuna Abhineri mwanakomana waNeri achiti: Haudaviri here Abhineri? Abhineri ndokudavira ndokuti: Ndiwe aniko unoshevedzera kuna mambo.
\v 15 Dhavhidhi akati kuna Abhineri: Ko iwe hausi murume wemhare here? Ndianiko wakafanana newe kuVaIsraeri? Wakaregereiko kurinda ishe wako mambo? Nokuti umwe munhu wakange apinda kuzoparadza mambo, ishe wako.
\v 16 Ichi chinhu chawaita hachina kunaka. NaJehovha mupenyu, maifanira kufa, nokuti hamuna kurinda ishe wenyu, muzodzwa waJehovha. Zvino chitarira, pfumo ramambo nechirongo chemvura chakange chiri kumusoro kwake zviripiko?
\p
\v 17 Sauro akaziva inzwi raDhavhidhi, akati: Ndiro inzwi rako here, mwanangu Dhavhidhi? Dhavhidhi akati: Inzwi rangu, ishe wangu, mambo.
\v 18 Akati: Ko Ishe wangu unoteverereiko muranda wake? Nokuti ndakaiteiko? Zvakaipa zviri mandiri ndezveiko?
\v 19 Naizvozvo zvino ishe wangu mambo chidonzwai mashoko omuranda wenyu. Kana ari Jehovha wakakukurudzirai kurwa neni, ngaapiwe chipo; asi kana vari vana vavanhu, ngavave vakatukwa pamberi paJehovha, nokuti vakandidzinga nhasi, kuti ndirege kugara panhaka yaJehovha, vachiti: Enda, undoshumira vamwe vamwari.
\v 20 Naizvozvo zvino ropa rangu ngarirege kuwira pasi kure naJehovha, nokuti mambo waIsraeri wabuda kuzotsvaka rutata rumwe, somunhu unovhima hwari mumakomo.
\p
\v 21 Ipapo Sauro akati: Ndatadza, dzoka hako, mwanangu Dhavhidhi, nokuti handichazokuitiri zvakaipa, nokuti upenyu hwangu hwakange huchikosha pameso pako nhasi; tarira, ndaita sebenzi, ndatadza kwazvo.
\v 22 Ipapo Dhavhidhi akapindura akati: Tarirai pfumo ramambo! Umwe wamajaya ngaayambukire kuno aritore.
\v 23 Jehovha unoripira munhu umwe neumwe kururama kwake nokutendeka kwake; nokuti Jehovha wakakuisai nhasi kwandiri, asi ndakaramba kutambanudzira ruoko rwangu kumuzodzwa waJehovha.
\v 24 Zvino tarirai, upenyu hwenyu sezvandakahukudza nhasi, saizvozvowo hupenyu hwangu ngahukudzwe naJehovha, iye andirwire pakutambudzika kwangu kwese.
\v 25 Ipapo Sauro akati kuna Dhavhidhi: Wakaropafadzwa iwe mwanangu Dhavhidhi; uchava nesimba, uye uchakunda kwazvo. Naizvozvo Dhavhidhi akaenda hake, naSauro akadzokera kumusha kwake.
